('behavioral', 'entry', 'general', null, 'teamwork', 'Tell me about a time you worked with a difficult teammate.', null, '["Focus on situation and your response", "Blame the teammate", "Say you never had one", "Keep it vague"]'::jsonb, 0, 'Use STAR: situation, task, action (your response), result. Stay professional.', 1),
